_sText:
This is my first map I have made for CS:S.  

It is a simple map that is small and maze like.

The bottom floor is coverd with a waist high water level and hides smoke grenades randomely strewen about the map.  Also the bottom floor is more of a mase and has meny dead ends the might hide a few wepon stashes here and there.  The top floor is almost the same but you can get lost a lot quicker on the top the on the bottom.  All the walls allow you to shoot though them.

The entier map is dark save for where you spwan thous giveing the map its name.

Max players is 40.

It is already bot enabled
